description: Another ambitious boy who would like to make it big in the capital city. He was from a small town in Southern Bohemia where he was deeply unsatisfied with local wages. His plan was to find a properly paid job and bring his girlfriend to Prague. And then start a family. I liked the plan and I wanted to help the dude. I knew a friend who was looking for a waiter so I offered our young man the job. He accepted it right away only to realize there was a catch. He couldn´t afford our mediation fee so we had to find a different way. He wasn´t very hard to convince that my naughty solution is the best option. I like family oriented guys, they are willing to do anything to help their loved ones. This guy tried very hard to make me happy and he did a pretty good job for a rookie. Money well-spent.
title: Dirty Scout 146
